data.description: One of the few gated communities in Tifton with protective covenants, come tour The Gates at Cypress Pointe!  This quiet neighborhood is located on the north side of town in close proximity to the hospital and corridor to I-75 and ABAC.  This home has three bedrooms and two bathrooms and was constructed with low maintenance a priority.  The kitchen is at the center of the home with an adjoining dining room, living room, large laundry room and a walk out patio in a quaint setting with a privacy fence.  The front porch also offers a great resting place with beautiful flag stone flooring.  Features of this home include cabinets with the soft close mechanism, granite countertops, stainless appliances, ceiling fans, 2 inch vinyl custom blinds and luxury vinyl planking throughout the home.  The larger bedroom has a beautiful tiled shower, soaking tub and a walk in closet.    The two car garage offers attic storage.  Builder will provide landscaping and an inground sprinkler system.
